T02TD3384E:54a-1: aa pa r'a dzi ta s'a dha nam /
T02TD3384E:54a-3: rnam par rgyal ma'i sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD3384E:54a-4: 'phags ma khros ma rnam par rgyal ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3384E:54a-5: rnam par rgyal ma ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma /
T02TD3384E:54a-6: lha rdzas kyi rin po che sna tshogs kyis mdzes ma /
T02TD3384E:54a-7: tshogs bdag rnam par mnan ma /
T02TD3384E:54a-8: g-yas pa thal mo sbyar ba'i tshul byas pa'i phyag go //
T02TD3384E:54a-9: g-yon na zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub snying gar 'chang ba'i phyag go //
T02TD3384E:54a-10: shin tu 'jigs par byed pa'i mche ba gtsigs shing drag pa'i zhal can ma /
T02TD3384E:54a-12: tshangs pa la sogs pa gdug cing mi bzad pa'i rnam pa'i lha rnams kyis bskor zhing /
T02TD3384E:54b-1: rnam par rgyal ma'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
T02TD3384E:54b-2: pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
T02TD3384E:54b-3: khams pa lo ts'a ba dge slong ba ris bsgyur ba'o//
